text: Disney XD is a Scandinavian TV channel of the American channel of the same name. The channel was launched 12 September 2009 and focused on kids and teens content. The channel closed on 31 December 2020 but it was relaunched on 29 May 2024. In Norway, the channel replaced Cinecanal on Allente. ==References== Category:Television channels in Europe
title: Disney XD (Scandinavian TV channel)
